# Ephemeral / generated pipeline artifacts — never commit (§11.4.10 / §11.4.30).
# pipeline_signed.sh generates the ed25519 keypair + signed ZIPs into a mktemp
# dir outside the repo and rm -rf's it on exit; these defensive ignores cover
# any stray local generation. PIPELINE_EVIDENCE.txt is intentionally tracked.
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.zip
*.bin
*.sig
ota-server
server.log
*.tmp
